io.github.miquelo.tools.packer

Interface PackerCommandResult


  • public interface PackerCommandResult
    Result of Packer command task execution. It can have four states.
    Succeed
    Execution finished successfully
    Ignored
    Execution was ignored due to initialization decision
    Failed
    Execution was failed due to Packer execution failure
    Command error
    Error was occurred due to command initialization error
    See Also:
    PackerCommandTask.get(), PackerCommandTask.get(long, java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit)
